data.title: 678 E 100 N #2, Enterprise, UT 84725
data.meta_description: Zillow has 37 photos of this $299,900 3 beds, 3 baths, 1,362 Square Feet townhouse home located at 678 E 100 N #2, Enterprise, UT 84725 built in 2022. MLS #24-247857.
data.text: Now available, newly built 2022, 2 level townhome, 1,362sqft, 3 bed, 2.5 bath, with a 1 car garage, No HOA. Like new. This unit has beautiful cabinets with granite counter tops and stainless steel GE appliances. LVP and Carpet flooring. Vinyl fenced backyard for privacy. The perfect starter home, second home or investment property. Tile roof with stucco and vinyl siding. This is a quality built townhome by Andrus Homes. Enterprise, UT is a small rural city in Southern Utah that is only 40 minutes from St. George or Cedar City. Close to Grocery Stores, Ace Hardware, Family Dollar, Restaurants, Gas, Schools, Medical/Fire Services. Schedule a showing today. Home is not furnished. Photos are from Unit #1. Each unit has 2 extra parking spaces in addition to the garage parking.
